org.afplib.afplib

Interface PGPRG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PGPRGImpl

    public interface PGPRG
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'PGPRG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • RG Length
    • Xm Oset
    • Ym Oset
    • PGorient
    • SHside
    • Pg Flgs
    • PM Cid

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getPGPRG()
